data.eml:eml: Identification of Haplothrips species from Malesia (Thysanoptera, Phlaeothripinae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Mound, Laurence A. (2019): Identification of Haplothrips species from Malesia (Thysanoptera, Phlaeothripinae). Zootaxa 4623 (1): 41-50, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4623.1.3
